    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated Double VANOS variable valve timing system. This specimen is mechanically superlative, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, precise shifts, paired with an M Variable Differential Lock that remains silent and responsive. The factory finish is flawless, and the interior retains its original matte texture without bolster wear. This is a turn-key, investment-quality example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated engineering.",
